                     <interp inst="t18111204-46-off253" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18111204-46-off253" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, from the person of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18111204-46-victim450" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Silvester
                        <interp inst="t18111204-46-victim450" type="surname" value="Silvester"></interp>
