                  , on the <rs id="t18111204-46-cd254" type="crimeDate">25th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18111204-46-off253 t18111204-46-cd254"></join>, a pocket book, value 6 d. and a warrant for the payment of one hundred pounds, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18111204-46-victim452" type="victimName">
